description.content: GitHub brings together the world’s largest community of developers to discover, share, and build better software. From open source projects to private team repositories, we’re your all-in-one platform for collaborative development.

og:description.content: GitHub is where people build software. More than 50 million people use GitHub to discover, fork, and contribute to over 100 million projects.
